{"tid":645730,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"鼠蹊部摸到有硬嘅淋巴核係咪正常？","createTime":"2018-04-28T12:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T17:26:03.000Z","uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5391e831478d9a0f283bf2315985a7b4efa00982","tid":645730,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"最近突然摸到鼠蹊部（生殖器官同大脾之間條隙）有粒好硬嘅野，我自己估係淋巴核，但又硬又推唔郁，附近都有啲好細嘅但唯獨嗰粒好大，唔知係咪正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我怕又係自己多心同埋又起啲毛隔離所以廢事睇醫生柒，因為成日都覺得自己病但睇醫生話只係正常野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca2249e1a3b1658d30a0b775a61a41bf0f5e5fc","tid":645730,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:12:15.000Z","msg":"粒野應該得0.5cm但硬過石春<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfd18fac3de7aad80511ed84d341a10320a3edc","tid":645730,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:13:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57f0a75df559addbc58e1a7cad03dff2e6f9699e","tid":645730,"uid":151354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:13:49.000Z","msg":"我之前有個fd都係咁"},{"pid":"44312ff53ed3fe4c009ece84c10aa779ef1efaa4","tid":645730,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57f0a75df559addbc58e1a7cad03dff2e6f9699e","tid":645730,"uid":151354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:13:49.000Z","msg":"我之前有個fd都係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:15:07.000Z","msg":"咁係正常野定係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n好怕死，所要想知清楚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a29537aadf4441991c9bbdf979ebbb1ad96fe4","tid":645730,"uid":42392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"57f0a75df559addbc58e1a7cad03dff2e6f9699e","tid":645730,"uid":151354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12: